---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Asteris Partners. Refer Asteris. Earn 25% on every sale."
  description="Asteris Partners is the referral program for the four Asteris plugins (WC, WP, Cart, Affiliates). 25% Year 1, 15% Year 2+ recurring, 60-day attribution cookie, cross-product credit, monthly Stripe Connect payouts. Built for agencies, content creators, and developers who already recommend the best WP/WC tools."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">â˜… Asteris Partners</span>
      <h1>Refer Asteris.<br>Earn on every sale.</h1>
      <p class="lead">25% Year 1. 15% Year 2+ recurring. One link across all four plugins. Built for agencies, content creators, and developers who already recommend the best WP and WC tools.</p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a href="https://pay.asteriscommerce.com/partners" class="btn-primary">Apply now â†’</a>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn-secondary">How it works</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="terms">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">The program in numbers</h2>
      <div class="terms-grid">
        <div class="term-card">
          <div class="term-label">Year 1 commission</div>
          <div class="term-value">25%</div>
          <div class="term-meta">on every sale</div>
        </div>
        <div class="term-card">
          <div class="term-label">Year 2+ recurring</div>
          <div class="term-value">15%</div>
          <div class="term-meta">on every renewal, forever</div>
        </div>
        <div class="term-card">
          <div class="term-label">Cookie window</div>
          <div class="term-value">60 days</div>
          <div class="term-meta">from each click</div>
        </div>
        <div class="term-card">
          <div class="term-label">Payout hold</div>
          <div class="term-value">30 days</div>
          <div class="term-meta">refund window</div>
        </div>
        <div class="term-card">
          <div class="term-label">Payout threshold</div>
          <div class="term-value">$100</div>
          <div class="term-meta">monthly, Stripe Connect</div>
        </div>
        <div class="term-card">
          <div class="term-label">Cross-product</div>
          <div class="term-value">4 plugins</div>
          <div class="term-meta">one cookie covers all</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="how-it-works" class="how">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">How it works</h2>
      <ol class="steps">
        <li class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <h3>Apply.</h3>
            <p>Fill out the partner application â€” name, email, audience, how you'll promote. We review every application personally and reply within 7 days.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <h3>Get approved.</h3>
            <p>Approved partners receive a unique referral link â€” <code>asteriscommerce.com/?ref=your-id</code> â€” that gives you credit on every Asteris plugin sale for 60 days from each click. One cookie, four plugins.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <h3>Connect Stripe.</h3>
            <p>One-click Stripe Express onboarding handles KYC, bank details, and tax forms. We never touch your financial data â€” Stripe does the heavy lifting.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="step">
          <div class="step-num">4</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <h3>Share your link.</h3>
            <p>Use your dashboard's ready-made tweet, newsletter, and one-liner templates â€” or write your own. Track clicks and conversions live.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="step">
          <div class="step-num">5</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <h3>Get paid monthly.</h3>
            <p>Approved commissions over $100 USD pay out on the 1st of every month via Stripe Connect. Funds arrive in your bank in 2-3 business days.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="founding">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="founding-card">
        <span class="founding-eyebrow">â˜… Founding Partners</span>
        <h2>25 launch slots. 30% lifetime commission.</h2>
        <p>The first 25 approved partners get the Founding Partner tier â€” locked 30% commission for life, early access to new modules, a private Slack channel with Nick, and co-marketing once your first referrals ship. Cap matches the Year 1 commission rate. Cute? Sure. Worth it? Massively.</p>
        <p class="founding-note">Founding Partner invitations go to organic advocates first (top 10), then open via the regular application for the remaining 15 slots at launch.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="rules">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">The honest fine print</h2>
      <div class="rules-grid">
        <div class="rule">
          <h3>Refund handling is silent.</h3>
          <p>If a customer refunds within the 30-day window, the pending commission silently disappears from your dashboard â€” no awkward "you owe us money" emails. Refunds after the window apply to your next pending balance, never your paid-out funds.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rule">
          <h3>Coupon conflict = 12.5%.</h3>
          <p>If a customer applies a coupon and clicks your link, you get 12.5% (half the normal rate). The store gives the customer a discount and you both share the cost. Fair to all sides.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rule">
          <h3>Self-referrals are blocked.</h3>
          <p>If you buy Asteris through your own link to grab 25% off, the system catches it and rejects the commission. Don't bother trying â€” buy at the Founder price like everyone else.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rule">
          <h3>No audience minimum.</h3>
          <p>We review every application by hand. We care more about how you'll promote than how many followers you have. Honest recommendations from a 500-follower newsletter beat spammy posts from a 50k bot account.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to apply?</h2>
      <p>Applications take five minutes. We respond within seven days.</p>
      <a href="https://pay.asteriscommerce.com/partners" class="btn-primary big">Apply for Asteris Partners â†’</a>
      <p class="muted small">Questions? <a href="mailto:support@asteriscommerce.com">support@asteriscommerce.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Brand tokens â€” Asteris parent palette (violet) */
  :root {
    --violet: #AA00FF;
    --violet-soft: rgba(170, 0, 255, 0.10);
    --violet-border: rgba(170, 0, 255, 0.32);
  }

  .container { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px; }

  /* Hero */
  .hero { padding: 96px 0 72px; }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block; color: var(--violet); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 64px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0 0 20px; color: #0a0a0a;
  }
  .lead { font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.55; max-width: 760px; color: #4a5568; margin: 0 0 32px; }
  .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--violet); color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px;
    padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 120ms, transform 100ms;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #BD2FFF; transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-primary.big { font-size: 18px; padding: 16px 36px; }
  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent; color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;
    padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid #d8dce6;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--violet); color: var(--violet); }

  /* Section titles */
  .section-title {
    font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin: 0 0 32px;
    color: #0a0a0a;
  }

  /* Terms grid */
  .terms { padding: 64px 0; background: #fafbfd; border-top: 1px solid #e0e3eb; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e3eb; }
  .terms-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
  .term-card {
    background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e0e3eb; border-radius: 10px; padding: 22px 24px;
  }
  .term-label {
    font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .term-value {
    font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--violet);
    line-height: 1.1; margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .term-meta { font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 4px; }

  /* How it works */
  .how { padding: 80px 0; }
  .steps { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: grid; gap: 28px; }
  .step { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr; gap: 24px; align-items: start; }
  .step-num {
    width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--violet-soft); color: var(--violet);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .step h3 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 6px; color: #0a0a0a; }
  .step p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4a5568; margin: 0; max-width: 720px; }
  .step code {
    background: #f4f6fb; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px;
    color: #4a5568; font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
  }

  /* Founding */
  .founding { padding: 64px 0; background: #0b0c10; }
  .founding-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(170,0,255,0.10), rgba(255,91,63,0.10));
    border: 1px solid var(--violet-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 48px 52px;
    color: #e8eaed;
  }
  .founding-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block; color: var(--violet); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .founding-card h2 { font-size: 36px; color: #fff; margin: 0 0 18px; line-height: 1.15; }
  .founding-card p { font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.65; color: #c8cbd0; margin: 0 0 14px; }
  .founding-note { font-size: 14px !important; color: #9aa0a6 !important; }

  /* Rules */
  .rules { padding: 80px 0; background: #fafbfd; border-top: 1px solid #e0e3eb; }
  .rules-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 28px; }
  .rule { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e0e3eb; border-radius: 10px; padding: 26px 28px; }
  .rule h3 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 8px; color: #0a0a0a; }
  .rule p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4a5568; margin: 0; }

  /* Final CTA */
  .final-cta { padding: 96px 0; text-align: center; background: #fff; }
  .final-cta h2 { font-size: 42px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #0a0a0a; }
  .final-cta p { font-size: 17px; color: #4a5568; margin: 0 0 28px; }
  .muted { color: #6b7280; }
  .small { font-size: 13px; margin-top: 24px !important; }
  .muted a { color: #6b7280; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 { font-size: 44px; }
    .lead { font-size: 18px; }
    .section-title { font-size: 26px; }
    .rules-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .founding-card { padding: 32px 28px; }
    .founding-card h2 { font-size: 28px; }
    .step { grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .step-num { width: 40px; height: 40px; font-size: 17px; }
    .final-cta h2 { font-size: 30px; }
  }
</style>
